      "title": "Gazette issued nominating Vajira Abeywardena as National List MP",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The elections commission today issued an Extraordinary gazette notification announcing Vajira Abeywardena as a national list MP of United National Party (UNP).",
        "The UNP nominated him and sent his name to the elections commission to replace the vacant seat after Ranil Wickremesinghe was elected the President."
